snippet.title: POPGOES - Party Room (OUTDATED)
snippet.description:
Not a trailer! This is in-game footage of the Party Room camera in Popgoes' Pizza, an upcoming Five Nights at Freddy's Fangame!

http://gamejolt.com/games/action/popgoes-pizza/64790/

There are no secrets in this footage at all! This is simply so we can officially "announce" our game on the /r/fivenightsatfreddys subreddit. 

Enjoy, and don't forget to get hype.

 -anti
